## Supported Values

### `privileges`

| Value | Description |
|---|---|
| `ALTER` | Allows altering keyspace schema |
| `AUTHORIZE` | Allows granting or revoking permissions |
| `CREATE` | Allows creating tables within the keyspace |
| `DROP` | Allows dropping tables within the keyspace |
| `MODIFY` | Allows `INSERT`, `UPDATE`, `DELETE`, and `TRUNCATE` |
| `SELECT` | Allows reading data with `SELECT` |

## Import
Import is not supported for {{.Name}} since the database will get reconciled based on the given
configuration whether the grants exist or not.
